Read Me\n\nUsage: Click the {{$:/plugins/FSpark/TiddlerScreenshot/remix-icon/screenshot-2-line}} icon on the Tiddler toolbar to Captures the currentTiddler as a PNG image.\n\nThe best practice is to put the screenshot button in the \"view toolbar\", which is the default way. This prevents the screenshot from getting blurred due to accidental moves when taking the photo. (Or implement several assistive \"screenshot\" tools, such as keyboard shortcuts, floating menus, etc.)\n\nIt is recommended to use [[CPL|https://tw-cpl.netlify.app/]] for installation to get the latest version. Contributors\n\n* whitefall: https://github.com/Zacharia2\n* FSpark: https://github.com/FSpark\n* dongrentianyu: https://github.com/dongrentianyu\n\n[img width=145 [https://img.thosefree.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/html2canvas-cover.jpg&720x405.jpg]]\n\n!! 4.
